cs.DL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on bibliometric analysis of scientific production, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The study also involves statistical analysis, which is related to computational complexity (cs.CR). Additionally, the study involves analysis of scientific disciplines and fields, which is related to cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the study involves analysis of organizational types, which is related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
